        <strong>Vitamin C — The Antioxidant Shield</strong>
        <p>Vitamin C accumulates in immune cells at concentrations 10-100x higher than plasma, reflecting its critical role in immune function. It supports neutrophil chemotaxis, phagocytosis, and reactive oxygen species generation during pathogen killing, while protecting immune cells from self-inflicted oxidative damage.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="info-card">
        <div class="info-card-ico"><Icon name="leaf" size={22} /></div>
