        <p>Black elderberry (Sambucus nigra) provides concentrated anthocyanins with demonstrated antiviral activity. A 2019 meta-analysis found elderberry supplementation reduced upper respiratory symptom duration by an average of 2 days. Most effective when taken preventively or at the earliest onset of symptoms.</p>
      </div>
